{"title":"【065】文本修饰","slug":"hell0-world13","date":"2022-10-02T01:45:59.000Z","updated":"2023-06-21T11:16:53.053Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hell0-world13.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"                text decoration                       文本修饰","covers":null,"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>text decoration</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"./mystyle3.css\">  \n</head>\n<body>\n    <h1></h1>\n    <p class=\"wb\"> \n        文本修饰<span id=\"more\"></span>可使用text-decoration-line,文本上方划线：over-line；文本中间：line-through;文本下方：underline\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        同一个文本可设置多个线条，通过text-decoration-line,设置多个值，中间用空格分开。如text-decoration-line: overlines underline<br><br>\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"sb\">\n        使用了超链接的文本就不要用underline装饰了，它自身带有下划线。<br><br>\n        装饰文本颜色通过text-decoration-color实现<br><br>\n        为装饰线指定风格通过text-decoration-style实现，属性值为solid，double,dotted,dashed,wavy。<br><br>\n        为线条设置厚度:text-decoration-thickness,值为auto,Px,百分比。 <br><br>\n    </p>\n</body>\n</html>","categories":[{"name":"CSS","slug":"CSS","count":30,"path":"api/categories/CSS.json"}],"tags":[]}